v.hk/gia/general/201502/12/P201502120356.htm|publisher=香港特別行政區政府新聞處|accessdate=2015-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151119024237/http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201502/12/P201502120356.htm|archive-date=2015-11-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>

